    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED RECORDING)</p>
    <p>EDDIE IZZARD: Cows go roo (ph). Sheep go meh (ph). Ducks go quack. Pigs go oink, all of them. Chickens go cockle-doodle-do (ph) unless you wedge a trumpet on their face.</p>
