    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED RECORDING)</p>
    <p>LULA: (Speaking Portuguese).</p>
    <p>REEVES: Even Lula's enemies agree that at 72, he remains a fighter. At that recent gathering in Rio, he certainly didn't sound like someone who's giving up.</p>
