    <p>PJ MORTON: Good to be here. Good to be here. Thank you for having me.</p>
    <p>MARTIN: Well, first of all, congratulations on the nominations. What is it like to be nominated? I mean, where were you when you found out? I mean, who calls you? Does your agent call you or, you know, how does that work?</p>
